<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>글쓰기</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <h1>🖊️ 새 글 작성</h1>
